Detailed Description

cvmx_l2c_ver_pp

L2C_VER_PP = L2C Virtualization ID PP Error Register

Description: records PPs associated with HOLEWR/BIGWR/VRTWR/VRTIDRNG/VRTADRNG interrupts.
